<subSubSection id="829C37AF91D0D1EC23D711C3E8FCB3F6" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="2F3D0B270A8E0C0D982DBF5FBDF4A62F" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7C7884BA032409F74D983A77D989614E" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">
New record: South Pirin Mt., Kalimantsi vill., 06.08-08.09.2002, pitfall traps, 1 w., leg. M. Langourov (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="8AC419EF0DC17CD11775BFA82B83D64A" captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F7727177" captionText="Figure 6. Temnothorax finzii, worker lateral: specimen from Kalimantsi vill.; scale bar 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.10.e83658.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/653856" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">6</figureCitation>
). Detailed occurrence data: 
<bibRefCitation id="14C2320D73A9C9C9D65AFE7AACD351B6" author="Lapeva-Gjonova, A." journalOrPublisher="Biodiversity Data Journal" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" refId="B7741022" refString="Lapeva-Gjonova, A., Borowiec, L., 2022. New and little-known ant species (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) from Bulgaria. In: Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." title="New and little-known ant species (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) from Bulgaria" volumeTitle="Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." year="2022">Lapeva-Gjonova and Borowiec (2022)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="7B0F3677D65FF7B9563C469E6CFA1E45" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" type="notes">
<paragraph id="7FE33333BD2162B1EE93A3E215816094" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A5327CC6E0ED3AE008D43F3B5059C804" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">
First record for Bulgaria. Extremely rarely reported species known from Italy and the Republic of North Macedonia (
<bibRefCitation id="FD4584E548AF42A422DD1369715CC25E" author="Bracko, G." journalOrPublisher="North-Western Journal of Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" pagination="10 - 24" refId="B7725718" refString="Bracko, G., Wagner, H. C., Schulz, A., Gioahin, E., Maticic, J., Tratnik, A., 2014. New investigation and a revised checklist of the ants (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) of the Republic of Macedonia. North-Western Journal of Zoology 10 (1): 10 - 24" title="New investigation and a revised checklist of the ants (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) of the Republic of Macedonia" volume="10" year="2014">
<normalizedToken id="42152803871494BAC7315850851AE81C" originalValue="Bračko">Bracko</normalizedToken>
et al. 2014
</bibRefCitation>
), as its presence in Anatolia is doubtful (
<bibRefCitation id="831203A62E4835BC3C2F8408DE4AFA88" author="Kiran, K." journalOrPublisher="Zoosystema" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" pagination="285 - 329" refId="B7725795" refString="Kiran, K., Karaman, C., 2020. Additions to the ant fauna of Turkey (Hymenoptera, Formicidae). Zoosystema 42 (18): 285 - 329" title="Additions to the ant fauna of Turkey (Hymenoptera, Formicidae)" volume="42" year="2020">Kiran and Karaman 2020</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
